: bold;font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体;background-color: rgb(255, 252, 244)">亲爱的热心人士：</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-autospace:ideograph-other;text-align:justify;vertical-align:"><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">你们好！我们是中南民族大学第三届研究生支教团的成员。</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">在</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">今年<span style="font-family:Times New Roman">12</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月份，</span></span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">我们欲</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">在</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">西藏自治区山南地区隆子县隆子镇新巴完小</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">学</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">建立第二个高原书屋</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">，所以想向热情且充满爱心的你们寻求一些帮助。</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;;"><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">“</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">高原书屋</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">”公益</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">项目</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">缘起于去年我校西藏支边志愿者寄给我校陈达云书记的一封信，信上承载着西藏山南错那县觉拉</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">一小</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">师生渴望建立一间高原书屋的心愿，这一心愿最终在陈达云书记的支持以及校内外爱心人士的帮助下得以实现，在西藏山南错那县觉拉乡觉拉一小，建立了首个高原书屋示范落成点</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">，这让雪域高原的看到孩子们感受到来自民大的爱意和温暖，享受到知识的快乐和满足！</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-autospace:ideograph-other;vertical-align:"><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">为了第二个高原书屋的顺利筹建，现</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">特向广大</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">充满爱心的民大校友发出倡议</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">，希望大家帮助我们</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">募集</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">资金、小学读物</span><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;">或其他学习用品</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">等，当然我们也会将大家爱心切实地传递到雪域高原的孩子们手中。以下是我们所需的物资：</span></p><p><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">所需物资一：</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">黑板</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">5<span style="font-family:宋体">块（长宽：</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">1.2*4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">米或</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">1.2*3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，价格</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">200~300</span><span style="font-family:宋体">每块）</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">所需物资二：</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">课外书籍，建议书目附于尾页（注有拼音的各类书籍最佳，</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 宋体">西藏特殊的孩子们语言还尚薄弱</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">此书目以外适合小学生阅读的文史<span style="font-family:Times New Roman">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">地理</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:宋体">自然的书籍也可以）</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-weight:bold;font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">所需物资三：</span><span style=";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;">其他学习用品</span></p><p><span style=";font-size:19px;font-f