籍！谢谢！</p><p style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; font-size: 12px; ; ; outline: 0px; ; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; "><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; font-size: 12px; ; ; outline: 0px; ; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; "><strong style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; ">【捐助方式】</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; font-size: 12px; ; ; outline: 0px; ; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; ">物资接收地址：山西省大同市浑源县西留村联校</p><p style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; font-size: 12px; ; ; outline: 0px; ; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; ">物资接收人： 刘校长（收）<br style="box-sizing: content-box; "/>邮编：037400</p><p style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 0px; font-size: 12px; ; ; outline: 0px; ; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; ">建议您先与我们私信联系，方便您的物资抵达，以及我们为您反馈求助落实详情。</p><p style="